These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, salsa, gospel, folk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, rose, tulip, amaryllis
House: wooden, art-deco, victorian, tower
City: london, nizza, hamburg, hannover
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, fuchsia, blue, apricot
 1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
 2. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##5
 3. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
 4. the person who growszinnia is the person traveling to nizza##1
 5. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 6. the person traveling to nizza is not to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##8
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is not to the left of the person who likes mauve##8
 9. the person who likes apricot is the fan of hip-hop##1
10. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the fan of salsa##5
11. the fan of salsa is in an even position##4
12. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
13. the tower house is not to the right of the fan of gospel##8
14. the person who likes blue is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5
15. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
16. the victorian house is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Music-Genre    | folk | salsa     | gospel     | hip-hop |
| Flower        | rose  | zinnia | tulip      | amaryllis      |
| House         | tower  | art-deco    | victorian | wooden       |
| City       | london | nizza   | hamburg      | hannover  |
| Color   | fuchsia      | mauve  | blue   | apricot      |

