There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, brazilian, spanish, japanese
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, blues, punk, soul
 1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 3. the dannemann-smoker is not to the left of the brazilian##8
 4. the montecristo-smoker is between the bolivar-smoker and the old-henry-smoker##2
 5. the montecristo-smoker is not the fan of punk##6
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the dannemann-smoker##5
 7. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the fan of jazz##8
 8. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the dannemann-smoker##5
 9. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
10. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
11. the brazilian is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
12. the fan of punk is not to the right of the fan of jazz##8
13. the spanish is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
14. the person driving the bus is the person who's birthday is in may##1
15. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the japanese##8
16. the fan of jazz is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8
17. the person driving the roller is the person who's birthday is in november##1
18. the person who's birthday is in november is not the bolivar-smoker##6
19. the person who's birthday is in december is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
20. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the montecristo-smoker##5
21. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4        |
