 9. the cape-cod house is not to the right of the person eating peach##8
10. the person eating cauliflower is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
11. the person who growsaconite is not to the left of the person who growsbellflower##8
12. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the wooden house##1
13. the person traveling to boston is not to the right of the craftsman house##8
